node.text:
Please tell me that I’m not the only one who loves salsa so much that I want to eat it like a soup. 😬 Well, I went ahead and made my favorite homemade salsa into a soup so I could have the best of both worlds. ☺️ Tap the link in mg bio to go see the recipe and how I turned salsa into soup! 👉 @budgetbytes 

#soup #souprecipe #soups #salsalovers #roastedveggies #homemadesoup #soupoftheday #veggiesoup #veganrecipes #veganrecipeshare 

https://www.budgetbytes.com/black-bean-roasted-salsa-soup/
